home finance
home finance is comprised of two key business segments: prime production & servicing and consumer
real estate lending. the prime production & servicing segment includes the operating results
associated with the origination, sale and servicing of prime mortgages. consumer real estate
lending reflects the operating results of consumer loans that are
secured by real estate, retained by
the firm and held in the portfolio. this portfolio includes prime and subprime first mortgages, home
equity lines and loans, and manufactured home loans. the firm stopped originating manufactured home
loans early in 2004 and sold substantially all of its remaining portfolio at the end of the year.
